      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, fellow car lovers! It\u2019s not every day you come across a real 'time capsule' like this one. I\u2019ve poured a lot of love into keeping this beauty in showroom-ready condition, and honestly, she still feels like she just rolled off the lot. Whether you're cruising on the weekend or just want something that turns heads at every light, this is the one. I\u2019ve kept her tucked away in the garage, meticulously cared for, and she\u2019s just waiting for a new home where she'll be just as pampered. Come grab a coffee and take a look\u2014you\u2019ll see exactly why I\u2019m so proud of her!",
